0x1.name: VeeCon 2023 Ticket #4522
0x1.description:
I Need Friends - Created By [Ed Balloon](https://twitter.com/Ed_Balloon)

This token is a verifiable ticket for admission to [VeeCon 2023](https://veecon.co/), which is a multi-day event exclusively created for VeeFriends & the Web3 community.

Time: May 18th - May 20th, 2023

Location: Lucas Oil Stadium in Indianapolis, IN USA

To commemorate VeeCon 2023, [VeeFriends](https://veefriends.com) is honored to collaborate with Artist, Musician, and Founder of Run ED Collection and Beauty Supply Is Out Of Du-Rags - Ed Balloon. Inspired by his experience at VeeCon 2023 in Indianapolis, Indiana, Ed has integrated the chorus of the song "I Need Friends" by Ed Balloon featuring Ed B "The Puppet" as the showcased artwork that includes 10 variations combining elements of black and white, color, and static. Ed hopes this art serves as a reminder of the necessity of friendship and coming together, starting with finding the Friend in You.

0x1.name: Shanghai: Open Edition
0x1.description: Ethereum, Evolved: Shanghai is a collection of two art NFTs celebrating the Shanghai/Capella upgrade, a technological milestone on the Ethereum roadmap that will simultaneously upgrade the blockchain’s execution and consensus layers to enable staked ETH withdrawals. The open edition depicts the theme of decentralization, a benefit of the Shanghai/Capella upgrade. By encouraging participation of larger numbers of validators, the Shanghai/Capella upgrade improves the network’s security by increasing decentralization.

0x1.name: V 2022
0x1.description:
This token is a verifiable ticket for admission to V at Scope Beach on December 1, 2022, in Miami, Florida. This ticket will harness the power of Web3 token-gating to grant you access to a celebration of art, culture, live musical performances, and more.

To be admitted to V at Scope Beach, attendees must hold this token and register it via tokenproof's mobile app. You will need to show proof of ownership via tokenproof at the door. 

Terms and Conditions Apply, US Only, For Ages 21+ - [https://vayner3.com/v-terms-conditions/](https://vayner3.com/v-terms-conditions/)

0x1.name: May 23, 2010
0x1.description:
Everyone has at least one day they hold dear. It may be a birthday, an anniversary, a moment, a memory.
SAVE THE DATE is an NFT project that lets you hold your DATE and continue to celebrate it forever.

Feel.
By creating 1/1 NFT DATEs, each representing 1 day over the last 50 years, we only need to ask which DATE means the world to you?

Celebrate.
After you secure your DATE, in the first year, your DATE will unlock 4 FREE art pieces made by well known artists and all integrate your DATE.
For our first drop, we are excited to announce a partnership with Amber Vittoria.

In addition to the art, DATE holders receive a Celebration Package worth hundreds of dollars of exclusive promotions and benefits from partner hotels, restaurants, and brands that would help you celebrate your cherished DATEs.
